high_descs: Go to the fridge, to your left.
Pick up the plate from the fridge.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left and look up at the microwave.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the counter between the stove and the microwave.
Put the plate on the counter, to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the fridge.
Pick up the plate from the top fridge shelf.
Turn right and go to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the plate and then take it out of the microwave.
Put the plate on the counter between the fridge and the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate on the counter between the fridge and the stove.

high_descs: Turn right and go the the from of the refrigerator.
Pick up the tray from the top right shelf
heat up the tray in the microwave then take out the tray.
go to the counter on your right.
Place the tray on the counter next to the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tray on the counter next to he spoon.
